        <updateDate>2009-02-02T21:32:45Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>State and Local Sales Tax Deduction Expansion Act of 2009 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow all individual taxpayers a tax deduction for state and local general sales taxes (current law allows taxpayers an election to deduct either state and local income taxes or sales taxes).</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
